data.description: Discover the allure of this incredible 2-story residence situated on a coveted corner lot in the famous Iron Mountain Ranch Community! This beauty displays a swaying shade tree, an easy-care front yard, & a 2-car garage. Be welcomed by the lovely interior boasting a generously sized family room w/backyard access on the main level & a spacious living room upstairs that opens to the kitchen. High ceilings, sleek wood flooring, abundant natural light, & decorative light fixtures are features you'll love. The heart of this home is the well-kept kitchen, fully equipped w/a plethora of wood cabinetry, ample counter space, a pantry, & an island w/a breakfast bar. Oversized main retreat showcases plush carpeting underfoot, a full bathroom w/dual sinks & a separate tub/shower, & a walk-in closet. The cozy balcony allows awe-inspiring mountain & desert views w/c promises a tranquil spot for relaxing. You'll love hosting fun gatherings in the private backyard w/a covered patio. Don't miss out!
